## ğŸ§© Problem #1: â€œWhy Canâ€™t I Click Anything?â€

Everything was loaded. Everything was visible. And yetâ€”no clicks.  
The settings menu simply refused to acknowledge my existence.

Why?

- The settings menu was on a CanvasLayer.
- It instantiated at game startup.
- Which meant: **it lived *under* the pause menu.**
- Even with `process_mode = ALWAYS`, it still lost the click war.

### â˜‘ï¸ Fix:
I bumped its CanvasLayer to Layer **2**.  
Suddenlyâ€”clicks everywhere. Victory.

